* Mouse can only distinguish whether a number > or <= 0

=== CONDITIONAL STATEMENTS ===
* Imperative                        * Mouse
if x > 0 then y = x                 X.[YX.:]
if x >= 0 then c                    X.1+[C]
if x = 0 then c                     1X.+[1X.-[C]]


